{
  "meta": {
    "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
    "name": "outro",
    "description": "根据胜负状态输出结局",
    "inputs": [],
    "outputs": [
      {
        "name": "result",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "prompt-build",
        "type": "PromptBuild",
        "label": "结局文本",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object",
            "defaultValue": {}
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "estimatedTokens",
            "type": "number"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "closing-header",
              "content": "黎明终于抵达海岬，风暴信标站的轮值结束了。"
            },
            {
              "type": "when",
              "id": "victory",
              "condition": "state.status == 'victory'",
              "content": "主灯熬过了最后一道黑潮。你站在还带着盐霜的铜梯旁，看见海面上两艘以上的船安全穿过礁带，港口回灯一盏接一盏亮起。值守员们虽然疲惫，却在晨光里终于笑了出来。你守住的不只是塔，而是整段海岸在暴风夜里的秩序。"
            },
            {
              "type": "when",
              "id": "defeat",
              "condition": "state.status != 'victory'",
              "content": "黎明到了，但代价比你预想更重。也许是燃料先枯了，也许是塔身在狂风里被撕开裂口，又或者你终究没能把足够多的船从雾墙里引出来。海面渐亮时，信标站仍立在崖顶，而你会记住这一夜每一次迟疑与每一道浪声。"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "shipsSaved",
              "source": "state.shipsSaved",
              "template": "最终救下船只数: {{items}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "fuel",
              "source": "state.fuel",
              "template": "剩余燃料: {{items}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "towerIntegrity",
              "source": "state.towerIntegrity",
              "template": "塔体完整度: {{items}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "crewMorale",
              "source": "state.crewMorale",
              "template": "士气: {{items}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "weather",
              "source": "state.weather",
              "template": "最后的海况: {{items}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "inventory",
              "source": "state.inventory",
              "template": "结局时仍在手边的物资: {{items}}"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "signal-out",
        "type": "SignalOut",
        "label": "输出结果",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "channel": "result"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "source": "prompt-build",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "signal-out",
        "targetHandle": "data"
      }
    ]
  }
}
